'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 11''' is the eleventh issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 6|''Star Wars'' (1977) 6]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 6}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 7|The Sword in the Star! Stave 2: Witchworld!]]" {{C|Part 2}}

*A contest to win a variety of ''Star Wars'' themed school supplies, including: PVC school sets; pencil boxes; tin maths sets; sets of pencils; sets of fiber-tip pens; pencil cases; and rulers. Prizes are provided by Helix, and seventy winners are chosen. To enter, readers must answer five ''Star Wars'' related multiple-choice questions.

